7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=c7c795b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"b7c2b71c57d98543dc8455d3b4f170e2c2cdc45f","tid":1702494,"uid":336374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:58:19.000Z","msg":"我最需要嘅佢離開左我。心好痛"},{"pid":"f470bcf8f1eafd82228beae1acee6aff126b2059","tid":1702494,"uid":268166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"我好想陪住你嫁 但你推開左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1719cde085b8b9fb9b81f1f3be2f64b8abb58b97","tid":1702494,"uid":91364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T18:32:40.000Z","msg":"又，其實唔拍拖有乜問題"},{"pid":"5ba3ba0aa9523a6d074df29a2f5df609526168f3","tid":1702494,"uid":120064,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T18:33:30.000Z","msg":"抑鬱咪去食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}